items.title: Billionaires are spending big to stop Zohran Mamdani's NYC mayoral bid
items.description: Bill Ackman, Ronald Lauder, William Lauder, Barry Diller and Dan Loeb have all made large donations to stop Mamdani. So have several non-New Yorkers.
